STAFF

AetherMUD is run by volunteer wizard staff who build zones, fix bugs, and
help players.

  wiz <message>       contact online wizards (wizard-only channel)
  ooc <message>       staff often monitor OOC for questions
  tell <staff> <msg>  mortals may tell online staff directly

Staff roles include Admin, Domain, Coding, and RP wizards. The who command
shows online staff with role tags.

SEE ALSO: wizardship, reporting, faq
